==其他==
本屬植物是某些[[鱗翅目|鱗翅目]]（包括[[稜巢蛾科|稜巢蛾科]]）昆蟲的[[幼蟲|幼蟲]]（例如：''[[Bucculatrix_quinquenotella|Bucculatrix quinquenotella]]''）的食物<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewildclassroom.com/biodiversity/problemplants/species/Ampelopsis.htm |title=Exotic, Invasive and Problem Plants |access-date=2019-03-06 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213235304/http://www.thewildclassroom.com/biodiversity/problemplants/species/Ampelopsis.htm |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

